sequenceDiagram
    participant C as gRPC Consumer
    participant G as GrpcMessagingApplication
    participant R as ReceiveMessageActivity
    participant M as MessagingProcessor
    participant P as PopMessageProcessor
    participant S as MessageStore

    C->>G: ReceiveMessage
    G->>R: receiveMessage()
    R->>R: 校验 Group、Topic、过滤器、不可见时间
    R->>M: popMessage / popLiteMessage
    M->>P: POP_MESSAGE
    P->>S: 查询可投递消息
    P-->>R: PopResult + ReceiptHandle
    R-->>C: 流式 ReceiveMessageResponse
